body.description: The SystemBuild Farmington 18” Wide Storage Cabinet is a stylish way to stay on top of your organization. The rustic barn style design and sleek tapered feet gives the look of an old weathered cabinet but the sturdy laminated particleboard and MDF make this cabinet the perfect piece to house your home office supplies, extra linens, seasonal clothing, nonperishable food and more! Open up the door to 4 spacious shelves, 2 adjustable, to fit items of differing sizes. The off-white woodgrain finish will bring a nice rustic appeal to your space. The Farmington Cabinet is recommended to be assembled and moved by 2 adults. A wall anchor kit is provided for extra safety and security. After assembled, this cabinet measures to be 71.9”H x 18.2”W x 15.8”D.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Farmington Bedroom Collection - Beautiful Rustic Style Give your home a beautiful rustic style makeover with the Ameriwood Home Farmington bedroom furniture collection. The Farmington farmhouse-style design highlights the rustic undertones you would see in an old barn or popular reclaimed pieces of furniture. The Farmington Queen Headboard is the perfect bedroom addition to enhance your home’s country style. The headboard has a textured finish and large decorative panels to give it an authentic farmhouse look. Complete your bedroom set with the Farmington Nightstand inspired by the farmhouse style, this rustic nightstand resembles a wooden barn door and adds a unique touch to your space. The collection also includes storage cabinets, headboards, 4 drawer and 6 drawer dresser, and nightstands that match your rustic décor. Color choices include rustic gray, natural, rustic, sandy pine, smokehouse, and weathered oak.

Farmington Living Room Collection Create a warm and inviting atmosphere in your home with the Ameriwood Home Farmington Electric Fireplace TV Console. Combine with the Farmington coffee table to add some country style to your living room. The Farmington collection was designed to catch the eye of your guests as they notice the charming rustic farmhouse-style design. Your guests will also love the old rustic look of the Farmington TV Stand. This TV Stand holds up to a 60” flat panel TV with a maximum weight of 135 lbs. Inspired by the weathered look of an old barn, this TV stand is full of character and brings a unique style element to your space. Other Farmington living room pieces include coffee table, entry way bench, storage cabinets, and craft table.

Farmington Rustic Headboard The Farmington Queen Headboard is the perfect bedroom addition to enhance your home’s country style. The sturdy laminated MDF and particleboard headboard has several wood grain finish options and large decorative panels to give it an authentic farmhouse look.Upon assembly, the Queen Headboard measures to be 48.3125”H x 65.75”W x 2.75”D. Farmington Rustic Storage Bench Create a warm, inviting entrance into your home with the Farmington Entryway Storage Bench. The rustic barn style design gives the look of an old weathered barn door. The rustic finish on the laminated particleboard adds to the rustic charm of this piece. Once assembled, the Entryway Storage Bench measures to be 19.8”H x 47.6”W x 15.9”D. Farmington Rustic Craft Table Add rustic charm to your den or craft space with the Ameriwood Home Farmington Craft Table. The rustic barn style design gives the look of an old weathered barn door. The woodgrain finish options on the laminated particleboard adds to the rustic charm of this piece. This Craft Table is finished on all 4 sides allowing you to work from either the front or the back. Once assembled, the Craft Table measures to be 30”H x 52.2”W x 23.6”D. Farmington Rustic Storage Cabinets The Farmington 31.5” Wide Storage Cabinet is a stylish way to stay on top of your organization. The rustic barn style design and sleek tapered feet gives the look of an old weathered cabinet but the sturdy laminated particleboard and MDF make this cabinet the perfect piece to house your home office supplies, extra linens, nonperishable food and more!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 17, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Sturdy and cute
reviews.reviewText: I purchased two of these for extra pantry space. I put one together by myself. It took about two hours. I suggest having someone to help. My husband helped with the second one and we had it put together in no time. I love the look of them and the space they provide. Definitely worth the money spent.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 14, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good Quality Product
reviews.reviewText: We had a small space where we wanted to add storage and this cabinet fit it perfectly. Everything was arrived in good condition. The directions were easy to follow and we are pleased with the sturdiness and look of the cabinet.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 13, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Annoying to put together but decent quality
reviews.reviewText: Directions were easy to follow. I was able to put it together without the help of my husband lol. Some screws are annoying to put in, definitely need a drill!! No way you can just use a screw driver. But beware, adjust your settings on your drill or you'll strip or break the boards. I only felt like giving up a few times. Luckily I was able to get it together. Surprisingly, it's very sturdy and has a cute farmhouse look to it. It works for the space i need it for. Using as a linen cabinet and has a lot of room to fill. Overall, really happy with my purchase considering the price point.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 14, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Grey, not white. Still nice!
reviews.reviewText: This shelf is definitely grey and not white, but I like the colour anyway. It has been holding up well and feels sturdy. It took two people about an hour to put together, mainly because it’s heavy and the pieces are big. The instructions weren’t too complicated. Definitely worth it!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 11, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Very nice storage cabinet. Good quality material and color is just perfect for my laundry room. Cabinet came in with small damaged dent on corner and customer service could not have been more helpful. Within 72 hours they mailed me a replacement part to use. Highly recommend company and products. I also bought the two door storage cabinet.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 25, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Dimensions are not clear
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. First, I specifically ordered this cabinet because of the size. I have a very narrow area in my bathroom I wanted to use this for with a 16" wide opening. Based on the picture, the dimension across the front would be 15.2" wide and the top supposedly has a piece with an overhang that makes it 18.2". THIS IS NOT CORRECT. The actual measurement across the front is 17" wide. It also does not show that there is a slight lip on the front panel that makes it wider than the back of the cabinet.Second, this is an extremely cheap piece of furniture. I knew it wasn't going to be the greatest quality based on the price and the description but but it's flake board and basically pressed cardboard. It really wasn't even worth the amount I paid for it. The pieces don't align well once it's put together and the magnets to hold the door shut do not line up with the metal part on the door. It wobbles and none of the screws get tight enough to keep it from wobbling - not to mention I would never want to tighten them too much because I would be afraid the pieces would split.Third, there is an imperfection right on the front.And last but not least, it took entirely too long to assemble. I'm not Bob the Builder but I'm also not inept. This should not have taken almost 2 hours to put together. The directions weren't great and some of the pictures were backwards.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 20, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Bought two of these and both were missing the same two parts plus one package was missing the entire package of hardware. Was able to request the missing parts on manufacturer’s website, but says it will take 7-14 business days to get them.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 3, 2023
reviews.reviewText: We bought on sale for Amazon prime day and it looks great! There were a couple spots where it was chipped but we didn’t return it. It wasn’t too noticeable while putting it together since the places were at the bottom.Would recommend! Company asks where we bought it from.
